## Evolution and Lineage

NexCache is a next-generation high-performance data storage engine. While NexCache has evolved into a distinct and advanced system with unique architectural innovations, its journey began with the foundational work of the open-source community.

This project is a successor and evolution of the following foundational works:
*   **Valkey Contributors**: For the core engine architecture and stability.
*   **Redis Contributors**: For the original data structure concepts and protocols.

NexCache acknowledges and respects the contributions of these communities. In compliance with the BSD-3-Clause license of its predecessors, this software retains the original spirit of open-source collaboration while pushing the boundaries of performance and feature-set beyond its initial origins.

